Package com.commander4j.db

Class JDBQMAnalysis

java.lang.Object
com.commander4j.db.JDBQMAnalysis
public class JDBQMAnalysis
extends java.lang.Object
The JDBQMAnalysis inserts rows into the APP_QM_ANALYSIS table. Each row in this table is used by the QM Analysis screen to allow the user to generate reports on Samples/Tests and Results.

See Also:
JDBQMResult, JDBQMInspection, JDBQMActivity, JDBQMDictionary, JDBQMTest
